            <div class="h2">
            <h2>Welcome to Anime Insight!</h2>
            <img src="../media/naruto2.jpg" alt="Second naruto image" class="image_2"/>
            </div>
            </br>
            <p>Anime Insight is dedicated to celebrating the vibrant world of anime. Founded by Sofia Martinez, an avid anime enthusiast, this site serves as a comprehensive resource for fans and newcomers alike. Our mission is to provide engaging and informative content about the rich history, diverse genres, and beloved characters that make anime a global phenomenon.</p>
            </br>
            <p>Here, you’ll find detailed insights into popular series, including classic hits and contemporary favorites like Naruto. Our goal is to create a welcoming space for everyone—whether you're a long-time fan looking to deepen your knowledge or a curious newcomer eager to learn more.</p>
            </br>
            <p>At Anime Insight, we believe that anime is not just entertainment; it’s a cultural experience that connects people across the globe. Join us as we explore the stories, art, and passion behind this incredible medium!</p>
